{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e678717",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふ～……やっと終わった……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bd9a70a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ティルのドラゴンの世話を手伝い、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.2",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bd9a70a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ようやく終わったところで俺は大きく息をついてその場に座り込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b2324d24",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "するとティルが俺の横へと歩み寄ってきてコートを脱ぐと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.2",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b2324d24",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "服をパタパタさせて汗ばんでいる体を冷やし始めた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3688a594",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "あっつ～！　でもキカイっちのおかげで助かった～！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ddba6fb7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや、これぐらい別に……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fd45de55",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "本当に助かったよ～、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.2",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fd45de55",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "でもすごく汗掻いちゃって……あっ、やばっ、めっちゃ服透けてるし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.0",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "578810be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その言葉に思わず俺はティルの方へと目をやると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.2",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "578810be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "確かに彼女の服は汗で濡れていて乳首が薄く透けて見えている。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b761696",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "これは見ちゃマズいと俺は慌てて視線を逸らすが見えたものは見えたもの。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52f19835",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の股間はすぐに反応してしまって、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.2",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "52f19835",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "どんどん大きくなっていってしまった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf4a92ed",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それをティルは目ざとく見つけて俺に囁きかけてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1944b158",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "んふふ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.2",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1944b158",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "キカイっちったら……反応しちゃってる♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "97e23f92",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いやっ……こ、これは……そ、その……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.0",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e65ff8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しどろもどろになる俺に、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.2",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e65ff8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ティルはニヤニヤしながら迫ってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8244b007",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "キカイっちが反応したのはどこだろ～？　んふふっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "284ef4b3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ご、ごめん……お、俺っ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52264435",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "いいのいいの♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.2",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "52264435",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "手伝ってくれたお礼に、あーしの身体……使わせてあげてもいいけどぉ？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37577e02",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "使わせてって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c96b691b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ティルの意味ありげな言葉に",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.2",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c96b691b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の頭の中は妙な妄想でいっぱいになってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.0",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "19d6ed7e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おかげで俺の性欲は大きくなる一方で我慢できなくなってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cbff7d89",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "どうする？　って聞くのも野暮かな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.2",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cbff7d89",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "そんなにおちんぽを勃起させちゃってるし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.4",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "cbff7d89",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "あーしの身体、味わってみるよね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dd6140c2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その問いかけに俺はコクリ頷いて、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.2",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "dd6140c2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "キツくなったズボンとパンツを脱ぐと",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.4",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "dd6140c2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すっかり勃起してしまったペニスを露わにさせた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "66d33b4c",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "それで……キカイっちは、あーしのどこを使いたいのかな？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ef530e86",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっと……それじゃあ……わ、脇を……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4b9de8f9",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "え～、脇に興奮しちゃうなんて♥　まじ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.0",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cd02b10e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "と言いつつもティルはおもむろに両腕を上げて脇を晒す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.0",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b0ba19ea",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "ほ～ら、キカイっち♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.2",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b0ba19ea",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "汗掻いてムレムレの脇だよ～♥　好きに使っていいよ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "36ed443e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それを見て俺の股間は更に脈打ってしまい、すっかりビキビキに勃起してしまった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c01d9d3",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "すごいっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.2",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c01d9d3",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "キカイっちのおちんぽ、ビンビンになっちゃってるぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a09eb976",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あからさまにそう言われると",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.2",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a09eb976",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "妙に気恥ずかしくなってしまうけれど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.4",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "a09eb976",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その反面ペニスはさらに反り返ってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "445f3fba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それを見つめながらティルは甘い声で誘ってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.0",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8c3df246",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "ほらほら～遠慮せずにキカイっちのおちんぽを",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.2",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8c3df246",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "グリグリ擦りつけていいんだよ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cce90837",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "煽るようなその言葉に俺は思わずゴクリと唾を飲み込んだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4c0964bd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すっかり剛直したペニスは",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.2",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4c0964bd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ビクンビクンと上下して亀頭からカウパー汁が",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.4",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "4c0964bd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "溢れてきてきてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.0",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7ed6d140",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "ほら～、遠慮しなくていいから～、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.2",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7ed6d140",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "あーしを使って気持ちよくなっちゃって～",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b9bdd37",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ティルの言葉に俺はドキドキしながら",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.2",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7b9bdd37",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "無防備な脇の下へと反り返ったチンポを",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.4",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "7b9bdd37",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆっくり近づけていった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4cb28f5d",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "はい、しーこしこ♥　しこしこ♥　くちゅくちゅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.0",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d360122f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺はティルに促されるまま彼女の柔らかな脇に勃起したチンポを擦りつけていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7430e174",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その感触はすごく気持ちが良くて、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.2",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7430e174",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "反り返った肉棒がビクンビクンと上下に跳ねた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3f60f26a",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "すご～い♥　キカイっちのおちんぽこんなに大きいなんて♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3f60f26a",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "それに熱くなって脈打っちゃって♥　んふっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.0",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53ba915c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あぁぁ……すごく気持ちよくて……くっ……ぅぅぅっ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5f8f47a7",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "もっとあーしの脇で気持ちよくなっていいんだよ♥　ほらほら♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.2",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5f8f47a7",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "遠慮しないで♥もっとおちんぽ、しこしこしちゃって♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4b5f1eee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺はそんなティルの言葉に煽られ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.2",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4b5f1eee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ついつい腰の動きを激しくさせて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.4",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "4b5f1eee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "反り返った肉棒をティルの脇に擦りつける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d386d228",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "あん♥　そんなにあーしの脇気持ちいい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.2",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d386d228",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "夢中になっちゃって♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "38785bfc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "すごくいい……ああっ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.0",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42b31b9a",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "いいんだよ～？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.2",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "42b31b9a",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "キカイっちの好きな時に～びゅびゅって出して気持ちよくなって♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ad7386be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ティルのその言葉に俺は一気に堪えきれなくなってしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.2",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ad7386be",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "射精したいという気持ちが高まってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "85e23cfa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな俺にティルが煽るような言葉を投げかけてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fedd3b01",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "キカイっちのおちんぽから、お汁がいっぱい溢れてきてる♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.2",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fedd3b01",
      "speaker": "ティル",
      "ja": "ああ、この匂い♥そろそろドピュドピュしちゃう？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.0",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7f162f6b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "チンポが脇に擦れる度にドクンドクンと脈動して",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.2",
